title: Geki Ai Buzoku No Se Kkusurangeji Dame Jungle De Itchau...!
description: [That's great .... you are already wet ...! I will make you happier] Megumi is a student majoring in Human Culture (Anthropological Culture) at the graduate school, she agrees to investigate locally in the rainforest as persuaded by the teacher. The wish to accompany the professor made her happy for a moment, but the rainforest has many dangers. Like how when she was attacked by a wild leopard, the Baltic Kuguru clan leader saved Megumi. When they started their daily life in the village, it was the custom of men and women to bathe together ...!? [Don't touch it ....] She was attacked in the most sensitive place by a powerful and gentle Baltic ... Even if she knew it wouldn't be, she still wished for it ... .
